  "text": "Registering new accounts is an essential part of SMF. Indeed, a customer ordering 6,000 follows expects 6,000 different accounts to follow his/her own account. Registration barriers are believed to be the highest challenges for offenders to circumvent [CITATION_1] . The decrypted traffic showed that the bots registered accounts either through a web browser using the Instagram web application or through the Instagram mobile application. In both cases, the requests relayed to register accounts are the same as those sent from a normal user. Emails created on the fly can be used to register accounts on Instagram because of the lack of identity verification by the OSN.",
  "correct_citation": {
